- 'Models introduced between 2010 and 2015' refers to carlines with an `introduction_year` between 2010 and 2015;
- 'Engines larger than 2.5 liters' refers to vehicle models with an `engine_displacement` greater than 2.5 liters.

- "Crown jewels" refers to the most valuable or prestigious items in a collection;
- "Command the highest average price" means the carline has the highest average base price;
- "Diverse lineup" indicates that the division has more than one carline.
